Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Coldit Community School to Don Hermenegildo Velasco Community School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 853
An Act Changing the Name of the Coldit Community School to Don Hermenegildo Velasco Community School
Section 1. The name of the Coldit Community School located at Barangay Coldit, Asingan, Pangasinan, is hereby changed to Don Hermenegildo Velasco Community School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
